docs {
  ## Update Location Comment
  แก้ไขความคิดเห็นของคลังสินค้า

  Updates an existing location comment. Only the author can update.

  ### Path Parameters
  - `id` — Comment ID

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "message": ""
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

